{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [1, 1, 1]}}}, "range": [0, 7], "size": 15, "font": {"id": "7080097079397192228", "path": "/Users/Zhuanz/Library/Containers/com.lemon.lvpro/Data/Movies/JianyingPro/User Data/Cache/effect/1654203/50957d5102cb4f2ea1459e140826eb0c/HelloFont ID JiangHuTi.ttf"}}], "text": "乐观的悲观主义"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [1, 1, 1]}}}, "range": [0, 5], "size": 15, "font": {"id": "7080097079397192228", "path": "/Users/Zhuanz/Library/Containers/com.lemon.lvpro/Data/Movies/JianyingPro/User Data/Cache/effect/1654203/50957d5102cb4f2ea1459e140826eb0c/HelloFont ID JiangHuTi.ttf"}}], "text": "情绪冷漠症"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [1, 1, 1]}}}, "range": [0, 5], "size": 15, "font": {"id": "7080097079397192228", "path": "/Users/Zhuanz/Library/Containers/com.lemon.lvpro/Data/Movies/JianyingPro/User Data/Cache/effect/1654203/50957d5102cb4f2ea1459e140826eb0c/HelloFont ID JiangHuTi.ttf"}}], "text": "生理性喜欢"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [1, 1, 1]}}}, "range": [0, 5], "size": 15, "font": {"id": "7080097079397192228", "path": "/Users/Zhuanz/Library/Containers/com.lemon.lvpro/Data/Movies/JianyingPro/User Data/Cache/effect/1654203/50957d5102cb4f2ea1459e140826eb0c/HelloFont ID JiangHuTi.ttf"}}], "text": "焦虑与内耗"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [1, 1, 1]}}}, "range": [0, 2], "size": 14, "font": {"id": "7080097079397192228", "path": "/Users/Zhuanz/Library/Containers/com.lemon.lvpro/Data/Movies/JianyingPro/User Data/Cache/effect/1654203/50957d5102cb4f2ea1459e140826eb0c/HelloFont ID JiangHuTi.ttf"}}], "text": "心理"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [1, 1, 1]}}}, "range": [0, 2], "size": 14, "font": {"id": "7080097079397192228", "path": "/Users/Zhuanz/Library/Containers/com.lemon.lvpro/Data/Movies/JianyingPro/User Data/Cache/effect/1654203/50957d5102cb4f2ea1459e140826eb0c/HelloFont ID JiangHuTi.ttf"}}], "text": "人格"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [1, 1, 1]}}}, "range": [0, 2], "size": 14, "font": {"id": "7080097079397192228", "path": "/Users/Zhuanz/Library/Containers/com.lemon.lvpro/Data/Movies/JianyingPro/User Data/Cache/effect/1654203/50957d5102cb4f2ea1459e140826eb0c/HelloFont ID JiangHuTi.ttf"}}], "text": "人格"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0.7333333333333333, 0.4392156862745098, 0.18823529411764706]}}}, "range": [0, 5], "size": 14, "font": {"id": "7080097079397192228", "path": "/Users/Zhuanz/Library/Containers/com.lemon.lvpro/Data/Movies/JianyingPro/User Data/Cache/effect/1654203/50957d5102cb4f2ea1459e140826eb0c/HelloFont ID JiangHuTi.ttf"}}], "text": "回避型依恋"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 20], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "你是不是也常常在深夜里反复回想白天的对话"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 11], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "担心自己的话有没有说错"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 12], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "别人一个眼神就会琢磨半天"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 9], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "明明没发生什么大事"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 8], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "却总觉得身心俱疲"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 13], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "你不是太矫情，也不是想太多"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 12], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "你只是拥有更细腻的感知力"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 18], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "这种感知力让你能捕捉到别人忽略的细节"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 14], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "也让你更容易感受到他人的情绪"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 19], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "在心理学上，这可能被称为\"高敏感特质\""}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 23], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "这类人往往拥有更丰富的内心世界和更强的共情能力"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 17], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "这或许源于你从小就习惯了观察和感受"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 27], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "在成长过程中，你可能比别人更早学会了留意他人的情绪变化"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 13], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "你的敏感不是缺陷，而是天赋"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 13], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "它让你能深刻理解他人的感受"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 13], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "也让你对世界有更细腻的体验"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 25], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "你能发现生活中细微的美好，也能在关系中更真诚地连接"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 14], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "试着给自己一点\"情绪缓冲带\""}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 17], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "当感到疲惫时，允许自己暂时离开人群"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 22], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "做一件能让你放松的小事，比如听首歌、看会儿书"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 30], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "也记得把你的敏感用在值得的地方，不必对所有人的情绪都过度负责"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 11], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "请记住，敏感不是你的错"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 17], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "你本身就很好，你的细腻是独特的礼物"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 23], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "接纳它，善用它，你会发现自己能更好地与世界相处"}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 74], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "Do you often recall the conversations during the day in the dead of night?"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 48], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "Worrying about whether you said something wrong?"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 57], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "Pondering over a single look from others for a long time?"}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 38], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "Obviously, nothing major has happened."}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 54], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "But you always feel physically and mentally exhausted."}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 0], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": ""}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 57], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "You're not being overly sentimental or thinking too much."}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 50], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "You just have a more delicate sense of perception."}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 74], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "This sense of perception allows you to catch details that others overlook."}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 59], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "And makes it easier for you to feel the emotions of others."}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 0], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": ""}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 71], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "In psychology, this may be referred to as the \"highly sensitive trait\"."}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 78], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "People with this trait tend to have a richer inner world and stronger empathy."}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 0], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": ""}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 76], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "Perhaps this stems from your habit of observing and feeling since childhood."}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 117], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "During the process of growing up, you may have learned to notice the emotional changes of others earlier than others."}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 0], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": ""}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 44], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "Your sensitivity is not a defect but a gift."}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 59], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "It enables you to deeply understand the feelings of others."}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 54], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "And gives you a more delicate experience of the world."}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 87], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "You can discover the subtle beauty in life and connect more sincerely in relationships."}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 0], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": ""}
{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 47], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "Try to give yourself a \"emotional buffer zone\"."}

{"styles": [{"fill": {"content": {"solid": {"color": [0, 0, 0]}}}, "range": [0, 76], "size": 5, "font": {"id": "", "path": ""}}], "text": "When you feel tired, allow yourself to temporarily stay away from the crowd."}
